        <section id="signup_beta" class="content">
          <div class="vessel">
            <h2>Get a seat in our spaceship !</h2>
            <form id="signup" action="/signup" method="post">
              <label for="signup_email">
                <p>
                  Our hosted version of WebRocket supporting the most popular
                  applications platforms is coming soon! Sign up with your email
